  "instructions": [
    "Heat butter in a large Dutch oven over medium-high heat.",
    "Add the Tandoori-Style Chicken and cook until browned on all sides, about 5 minutes.",
    "Remove the chicken from the pot and set aside.",
    "Add the beef broth, diced carrots, and diced potatoes to the pot.",
    "Bring the mixture to a boil, then reduce the heat to medium-low and simmer for 10 minutes.",
    "Add the frozen peas, bouillon cubes, salt, and black pepper to the pot.",
    "Return the chicken to the pot and simmer for an additional 5 minutes.",
    "Serve the stew hot, garnished with chopped fresh parsley."
